sections.heading: of trustees; certification of results
sections.text: For any sanitary and improvement district, the county clerk or election commissioner shall certify the results of the election to the district.SourceLaws 1976, LB 313, § 16;Laws 1977, LB 228, § 3;Laws 1982, LB 359, § 3;Laws 1986, LB 483, § 2;Laws 1987, LB 652, §
